@Node History
@{b}Version	Date		What was changed@{ub}
 1.0	19-Jan-96	first release

 1.1	28-Mar-96	no more dos requesters
			password request on active screen
			ask pack request on active window
			flush temporary directory at startup
			now files/patterns are supported as clients
			rewritten preferences editor
			support for locale.library
			added patch to OpenFromLock()

 1.2	22-May-96	client name with spaces now works
			added menus
			added arguments/tooltypes
			window refersh with asl requesters
			preferences editor now should work on MC68000,
				kickstart 2.x and asl.library V36
			refusing tasks (NT_TASK)

 1.3	12-Jun-98	reassembled with new XPK includes
			disabled USER packer which hangs preferences
@EndNode
